Text:
The reason why I'm only uploading Zygor and (eventually) Dugi is because those are the most popular leveling addons. I've had multiple requests for Dugi, and everyone loves Zygor. 

The other addons that have been requested are OUTDATED (they were built for Cataclysm).

If there are any further addon requests, I will promptly ignore them.
I'll upload the new version tomorrow.
